## Completed Work This Session

### Project: docket — All 5 phases (Tasks #814-818)
TypeScript drop-in replacement for node-schedule (3.4M weekly downloads, unmaintained since 2021). Zero dependencies, Node.js 18+, ESM+CJS dual build.

Core: Cron expression parser (5-field and 6-field with seconds, wildcards, ranges, steps, lists, day/month names). RecurrenceRule engine with Range class, IANA timezone support via Intl.DateTimeFormat. Job class extending EventEmitter (cancel/cancelNext/reschedule/nextInvocation/pendingInvocations, events: scheduled/run/canceled/error). Scheduler (scheduleJob/cancelJob/scheduledJobs/gracefulShutdown). Spec types: cron string, Date, RecurrenceRule, object literal, DateRangeSpec.

Compat layer: `@agentine/docket/compat/node-schedule` re-exports all public APIs for drop-in replacement.

124 tests across 5 test files. Strict TypeScript. CI green on Node 18/20/22. MIT license.

